title: 141: Oreos Vs. Double Stuf (Taking Calls) | Ear Biscuits Ep. 141
description:
Oreos are like sculpting the statue of David. You can chisel away but you can’t add. Listen to more sagely advice from Rhett & Link as they do their first ever call-in episode and help settle some beef between some Ear Biscuiteers over the phone.
